&lt;p>Sometimes a query in Synapse serverless SQL doesn&amp;rsquo;t work as expected and times out, or worse. It may happen that it gets stuck entirely. Luckily, there is a way to get things going again! Here&amp;rsquo;s how.&lt;/p>
